vych-332501.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、拒絕成為歐亞經濟共同體成員國<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-passes-an-anti-customs-union-resolution-333730.html|title=EuroMaidan passes an anti-Customs Union resolution|publisher=基輔郵報|date=2013-12-15|language=en|accessdate=2014-07-13|archive-date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627050941/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-passes-an-anti-customs-union-resolution-333730.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。示威运动其後漫延至乌克兰全境，又演變成親俄和反俄人士的武裝衝突。親俄人士反對烏克蘭親歐盟示威運動<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/party-of-regions-communist-party-banned-in-ivano-frankivsk-and-ternopil-regions-335655.html | title=Party of Regions, Communist Party banned in Ivano-Frankivsk and Ternopil regions | work=Kyiv Post | date=2014-01-27 | language=en | accessdate=2014-07-13 | archive-date=2014-06-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627220450/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/party-of-regions-communist-party-banned-in-ivano-frankivsk-and-ternopil-regions-335655.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/activity-of-regions-party-communist-party-yanukovychs-portraits-banned-in-drohobych-337297.html | title=Activity of Regions Party, Communist Party, Yanukovych's portraits banned in Drohobych | work=Kyiv Post | date=2014-02-21 | language=en | accessdate=2014-07-13 | archive-date=2014-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629054337/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/activity-of-regions-party-communist-party-yanukovychs-portraits-banned-in-drohobych-337297.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，又反對烏克蘭加入[[欧盟|欧盟]]和[[北约|北约]]。但是，烏克蘭最後仍與歐盟簽署了推遲已久的自由貿易協定。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140627_eu_ex_ussr_pacts.shtml| title=烏克蘭與歐盟簽署貿易協定| publisher=紐約時報中文網| accessdate=2014-06-30| archive-date=2014-06-30| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630025837/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2014/06/140627_eu_ex_ussr_pacts.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>

